OL,3,CUK running out of options for offshore
OL,4,Cenergy 'just transition' ` report
OL,6,FThe UK will fail to achieve a "just
OL,7,Fand fair" transition by 2030 unless
OL,8,Fthere is urgent alignment across the
OL,9,Fpolitical spectrum to sustain offshore
OL,10,Fenergy industry jobs and investment, a
OL,11,Fstudy has found.
OL,13,FExperts at Robert Gordon University
OL,14,Fanalysed more than 6,560 pathways for
OL,15,Fthe industry between now and 2030,
OL,16,Fconcluding that political decisions
OL,17,Frather than market forces will
OL,18,Finfluence the size of the workforce.
