OL,3,CUK running out of options for offshore
OL,4,Cenergy 'just transition' ` report
OL,6,FOf the thousands of scenarios
OL,7,Fanalysed, less than 0.3% could be
OL,8,Fconsidered a "just and fair"
OL,9,Ftransition, their report found.
OL,11,FProfessor Paul de Leeuw said Scotland
OL,12,Fwould be disproportionately impacted
OL,13,Fwith changes in the offshore workforce
OL,14,Fand supply chain, as a high number of
OL,15,Foffshore jobs are concentrated around
OL,16,FAberdeen.
