OL,4,Cenergy 'just transition' ` report
OL,6,FOil and gas production is currently
OL,7,Fexpected to decline by around 40% by
OL,8,F2030.
OL,10,FProf de Leeuw said: "The UK still has
OL,11,Fa unique opportunity to create a new
OL,12,Fenergy future.
OL,14,F"Accelerating the re-purposing of the
OL,15,FNorth Sea as a world-class, multi-
OL,16,Fenergy basin will ensure the sector
OL,17,Fcan power the country for decades to
OL,18,Fcome. The prize for the UK to get this
OL,19,Fright is enormous.
