OL,6,FScotland's Net Zero and Energy
OL,7,FSecretary Mairi McAllan said:
OL,8,F"Scotland's energy transition presents
OL,9,Fan era-defining opportunity for our
OL,10,Feconomy and people: delivering on our
OL,11,Fclimate obligations, safeguarding our
OL,12,Fenergy security and ensuring a fair
OL,13,Fand just energy transition for our
OL,14,Fworkforces and the communities they
OL,15,Fsupport.
OL,17,F"By working together, with absolute
OL,18,Fclarity of purpose, we will unlock the
OL,19,Fvast potential. Indeed, the transition
OL,20,Fis already happening with Scotland
OL,21,Ffast becoming a renewables powerhouse.
