OL,10,Fin our transformation of the energy
OL,11,Findustry, with #100 billion investment
OL,12,Fin green industries supporting up to
OL,13,F725,000 jobs by 2030.
OL,15,F"Much of the transferable expertise
OL,16,Ffrom offshore energies such as oil and
OL,17,Fgas will be crucial for the transition
OL,18,Fto net zero ` and our Green Jobs Plan
OL,19,Fwill ensure we have the sufficient
OL,20,Fskills to tackle emerging and future
